&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This should have been fixed by &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-17794&quot; title=&quot;UBSAN: array-index-out-of-bounds errors&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-17794&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-17794&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, right?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="426969" author="emoly.liu" created="Thu, 5 Sep 2024 02:35:59 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The Maloo testing results showed this failure only happened on client Ubuntu 24.04 in the past half year, but not Ubuntu 22.04. So it should be related to the difference between the kernels.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
